 was no improvements, you know, in them days. I mean, you had a leakage, you got a plumber, and that kind of thing, but there was no improvements. You just got a house and it had to stay as it was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8923336 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13134467\charrsid16010518 This lady, Alice Anne, was not responsible for you as children?
