Your mother mended the family's clothes and also you were grateful for clothes from the doctor's?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16384952 EO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13134467\charrsid16010518 Yes. Dr. Hall, I believe.
